data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bed 2 bath Cape cod home nestled on a wooded 2.44 Acres. Enter down the paved driveway at the end of the driveway is a large 2 car detached garage. In the back of the home is a covered patio area. Great for entertaining! The front porch also has a covered patio great for sipping on your morning coffee.  Enter through the front door into the living room. Head on down to the dinning room and turn right to this spacious kitchen. On the main floor is 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. The laundry room is inside this large full bathroom.   Head on down to the full unfinished basement with high ceilings. Here you have a blank canvas to turn this into whatever you'd like. The new oil heater is down in the basement along with the oil tank.  Head upstairs to 2 more bedrooms and a full bathroom. Septic was just updated last year along with the well.  Endless possibilities here with this property keep the 2.44 ACRES or subdivide. Don't miss out on seeing this home today! professional photos coming soon
